data.description: A must see! This is a beautiful 3bdrm, 2.5 bath, 2,207 sq ft. home with a 2 car garage built in 2009. Beautiful glass front door opens to a large living room, grand room and office in the the front room. Kitchen features a stainless steel farm sink, ss appliances, pantry and eating nook. The enclosed sunroom overlooks the covered redwood deck. The master has double sinks, Jacuzzi tub and a separate shower. Walk in closets. The Jack n Jill bathroom adjoin the 2 bedrooms on the opposite side of the house. Workshop included. Crepe Myrtles line the driveway. No restrictions.
